This paper deals with data integration and management, specifically focusing on entity resolution and consolidation. The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and truth discovery methods, which are commonly used in the fields of database management (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of scalability, which is a common concern in the field of cryptography (cs.CR).
